snippet: The Blackbirds won a rematch of last season’s championship game to earn another spot in the N.C.A.A. tournament field.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Long Island University defeats Robert Morris, 90-73, for its second consecutive Northeast Conference title; other college basketball results noted.
lead_paragraph: The Blackbirds won a rematch of last season’s championship game to earn another spot in the N.C.A.A. tournament field.
